%N A395874 Number of oriented polyominoes in the {5,5} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%C A395874 For oriented polyominoes, chiral pairs are counted as two.
%H A395874 <a href="https://oeis.org/wiki/PF-Non-Euclidean">Wiki page indexing sequences related to non-euclidean polyforms</a>
%F A395874 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of oriented {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q. In this case, P{p,oo} = A005038.
%t A395874 (* Cf. A394862 with p=5 and q=5. *)
%Y A395874 Cf. A005038, A393725, A394862.
